0. reference 
1) https://github.com/awslabs/amazon-kinesis-video-streams-producer-sdk-cpp/blob/master/docs/linux.md
2) https://github.com/awslabs/amazon-kinesis-video-streams-producer-sdk-cpp

1. aws ec2 instance 생성 및 접속


2. 기본적인 설정 
$ sudo apt-get update 
$ sudo apt-get install pkg-config
$ sudo apt-get install cmake
$ sudo apt-get install m4 


3. 다운로드 
$ git clone https://github.com/awslabs/amazon-kinesis-video-streams-producer-sdk-cpp.git


4. 디렉토리 생성 및 이동
$ mkdir -p amazon-kinesis-video-streams-producer-sdk-cpp/build
$ cd amazon-kinesis-video-streams-producer-sdk-cpp/build


5. 필요 라이브러리 설치
$ sudo apt-get install libssl-dev libcurl4-openssl-dev liblog4cplus-dev libgstreamer1.0-dev libgstreamer-plugins-base1.0-dev gstreamer1.0-plugins-base-apps gstreamer1.0-plugins-bad gstreamer1.0-plugins-good gstreamer1.0-plugins-ugly gstreamer1.0-tools


6. 디렉토리 이동 
$ cd .. 


7. JNI 설치 
$ cmake -DBUILD_JNI=TRUE

* could not find JNI error가 발생하는 경우  -> export JAVA_INCLUDE_PATH2='/usr/java/<JDK_VERSION>/include'


8. Gstreamer plugin 설치 사전 작업 
$ sudo apt-get install -y openjdk-8-jdk
$ sudo apt-get install -y default-jdk
$ export JAVA_HOME=/usr/lib/jvm/java-8-openjdk-amd64


9. 디렉토리 이동
$ cd build


10. Gstreamer plugin 설치  
$ cmake -DBUILD_GSTREAMER_PLUGIN=TRUE ..


11. 디렉토리 이동
$ cd ..


12. file make 
$ make 


13. path setting 
$ export GST_PLUGIN_PATH=`pwd`
$ export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=`pwd`/open-source/local/lib


14. plugin information check 
$ gst-inspect-1.0 kvssink


15. AWS_ACCESS_KEY, AWS_SECRET_KEY setting
$ export AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID=AKIA4Q5UCPKXXDZ7QXEQ
$ export AWS_SECRET_KEY=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


16. region setting
$ export AWS_KVS_CACERT_PATH=Kinesis-video-webrtc-native-build/certs/cert.pm
$ export AWS_DEFAULT_REGION=ap-northeast-1 

17. 가능한 media device 조회 
$ sudo gst-device-monitor-1.0


18. audio drivers 설치 
$ apt-get install libasound2-dev


19. 
$ gst-launch-1.0 -v v4l2src device=/dev/video0 ! videoconvert ! video/x-raw,format=I420,width=640,height=480,framerate=30/1 ! x264enc  bframes=0 key-int-max=45 bitrate=500 tune=zerolatency ! video/x-h264,stream-format=avc,alignment=au ! kvssink stream-name=jaedong_videostream storage-size=128 access-key="AKIA4Q5UCPKXXDZ7QXEQ" secret-key="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"


20. 설치 directory 조회
$ which gst-launch-1.0   # path에 anaconda가 포함되어 있으면 안됨 ..
